Introduction

This webpage presents an exploratory visualization of wildfire occurrences in Portugal during 2024, based on the national fire database.

The objective is to visualize fire activity spatially using three complementary approaches:

Clustered markers â€“ to visualize spatial concentration

Proportional circle markers â€“ scaled by burned area

Heatmap â€“ to highlight fire density patterns

The data used include:

Geographic coordinates (WGS84)

Burned area (AreaTotal)

Fire year (Ano = 2024)

fogos_2024 <- readRDS("fogos_2024.rds")
